NAME
       LessTif



SYNOPSIS
       LessTif is a free replacement for OSF/Motif®.

       As with Motif®, LessTif consists of a widget set, a window
       manager, and a UIL implementation (libMrm and the UIL com­
       piler).   In  LessTif,  our  main area of attention is the
       widget set.  We also have a working  window  manager  mwm;
       but UIL is not under very active development.

